ğŸ— Game Structure (Classes Overview)
Class Name	Purpose
GlobalWarGame	Main class: starts game, loops turns, handles I/O
Country	Represents each country: resources, military, regions
Region	Represents regions: owner, resources
AIPlayer	Controls AI country behavior
Event	Represents random world events
âœ… Example Session
=== WELCOME TO GLOBAL WAR TERMINAL EDITION ===
Enter your country name: Atlantis

Choose your starting region:
1. North America
2. South America
3. Europe
4. Asia
5. Africa
6. Oceania
> 3

=== YOUR TURN ===
Choose an action:
1. Build Military Units
2. Expand into new region
3. View Country Status
4. End Turn
> 1
Choose unit to build:
1. Army (Cost: 10 resources)
2. Navy (Cost: 15 resources)
3. Air Force (Cost: 20 resources)
> 1
Army built!
